{
"#name"
:
{
"install"
:
null
,
"en"
:
"Cross-platform installer for software, skills, and more"
,
"cn"
:
"跨平台安装器，支持软件、skill 等安装"
}
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Cross-platform installer — query and install software and skills, with interactive selection, CI/CD auto best-match, or structured output for AI agents"
,
"cn"
:
"跨平台安装器，查询并安装软件和 skill —— 支持交互式选择、CI/CD 自动最佳匹配、AI Agent 结构化输出"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x install [policy] [software]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x install --best <software>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x install --withtool <tool> <software>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x install --search <keyword>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x install --printinfo <software>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x install --printcmd <software>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x install --env"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"x i 是 x install 的简写，功能完全一样。\nx i bun 等同于 x install bun。\n"
,
"en"
:
"x i is shorthand for x install — identical in every way.\nx i bun is the same as x install bun.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"探索安装的推荐路径：\n1. x install --ls — 列出 install 模块收录的所有软件（支持 --tsv 输出）\n2. x install — 不加参数，打开 fzf 交互界面，搜索浏览所有软件和 skill\n3. x install <软件名> — 列出该软件的所有安装方法，交互选择\n4. x install <前缀>/<软件名> — 前缀直达，跳过选择（如 brew/jq、best/bun）\n"
,
"en"
:
"Recommended exploration path:\n1. x install --ls — list all recorded software (supports --tsv output)\n2. x install — no arguments opens interactive fzf UI to browse all software and skills\n3. x install <name> — lists all install methods for the software, pick interactively\n4. x install <prefix>/<name> — skip selection with prefix (e.g. brew/jq, best/bun)\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"前缀格式：包管理器/软件名\nbrew/jq、apt/git、npm/express、pip/httpie、cargo/ripgrep\nsys/bun — 系统包管理器\nbest/jq — 自动选最佳方法\nskill/anthropics/pptx — 通用 skill\nclawhub/skill-vetter — clawhub.ai 平台 skill\n"
,
"en"
:
"Prefix format: package_manager/software\nbrew/jq, apt/git, npm/express, pip/httpie, cargo/ripgrep\nsys/bun — system package manager\nbest/jq — auto-select best method\nskill/anthropics/pptx — general skill\nclawhub/skill-vetter — clawhub.ai platform skill\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"非交互安装（CI、脚本）用 --best、--sys、--withtool：\nx install --best bun — 按优先级自动选最佳方法\nx install --sys bun — 用系统包管理器\nx install --withtool brew bun — 用指定包管理器\nx install --best --priority brew,apt bun — 自定义优先级\n三个子命令都支持批量安装和 --printcmd（只打印不执行）：\nx install --best --printcmd bun vim\n"
,
"en"
:
"Non-interactive install (CI, scripts) with --best, --sys, --withtool:\nx install --best bun — auto-select by priority\nx install --sys bun — use system package manager\nx install --withtool brew bun — use specified package manager\nx install --best --priority brew,apt bun — custom priority\nAll three support batch install and --printcmd (print without executing):\nx install --best --printcmd bun vim\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"安装 skill 用 skill/ 或 clawhub/ 前缀：\nx install skill/anthropics/pptx\nx install clawhub/skill-vetter\n默认装到全局环境。版本控制和项目隔离用 x skill：https://x-cmd.com/mod/skill\n"
,
"en"
:
"Install skills with skill/ or clawhub/ prefix:\nx install skill/anthropics/pptx\nx install clawhub/skill-vetter\nSkills go to the global environment by default. For version control or project isolation, use x skill: https://x-cmd.com/mod/skill\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"claude-code、openclaw 等 AI Agent 工作流：\n1. x install --search <关键词> — 从 apt、brew、npm、skills.sh、clawhub.ai 聚合搜索\n2. x install --printinfo <软件> — 查看详细信息和所有安装方法\n3. x install --best --printcmd <软件> — 预览安装命令，确认后再执行\n结果支持 --json、--tsv、--csv 输出。\n"
,
"en"
:
"AI Agent (Claude Code, OpenClaw, etc.) workflow:\n1. x install --search <keyword> — aggregate search across apt, brew, npm, skills.sh, clawhub.ai\n2. x install --printinfo <software> — view details and all install methods\n3. x install --best --printcmd <software> — preview install command, then execute\nOutput supports --json, --tsv, --csv.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"claude-code、openclaw 等 AI Agent 环境探测：\nx install --env — 获取平台、架构、发行版等系统信息\nx install --available-tool — 列出所有支持的包管理器\nx install --available-tool --installed — 仅显示已安装的包管理器\n两个子命令都支持 --json、--tsv、--csv 输出。\n"
,
"en"
:
"AI Agent (Claude Code, OpenClaw, etc.) environment probing:\nx install —env — get platform, architecture, distro info\nx install --available-tool — list all supported package managers\nx install --available-tool --installed — show only installed package managers\nBoth support --json, --tsv, --csv output.\n"
}
]
,
