"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"默认查找收录的安装方法。加 --direct 不查找收录的安装方法，直接调用包管理器：\nx install --withtool brew bun — 查找 brew 安装 bun 的收录方法\nx install --withtool brew --direct bun — 直接用 brew 安装 bun\n"
,
"en"
:
"By default, looks up recorded installation methods. Use --direct to skip and call the package manager directly:\nx install --withtool brew bun — look up recorded brew method for bun\nx install --withtool brew --direct bun — directly install bun via brew\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --withtool brew vim bun"
,
"en"
:
"Install vim and bun using brew"
,
"cn"
:
"使用 brew 安装 vim 和 bun"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --withtool brew --printcmd vim bun"
,
"en"
:
"Print brew install commands for vim and bun without executing"
,
"cn"
:
"打印 brew 安装 vim 和 bun 的命令但不执行"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --withtool brew --direct bun"
,
"en"
:
"Directly install bun via brew (skip recorded methods)"
,
"cn"
:
"直接用 brew 安装 bun（不查找收录的安装方法）"
}
]
}
